        "cooktime": "30",
        "end-pic": "recipeimages/paneer-bhurji-gravy-end.jpg",
        "shortDesc": "Paneer Bhurji is a delicious recipe of crumbled cottage cheese which goes best with plain chapati or paratha or pao. In this recipe, crumbled paneer will be cooked in onion, ginger, garlic, tomato based creamy sauce with some flavorful spices. This paneer bhurji gravy will take very less time to cook. Try this recipe in your kitchen and let me know how it turned out for you.",
        "blog-type": "rb",
