        "completionStatement": "Your egg chicken roll is ready ...",
        "keywords": "egg, chicken, roll, snacks, street food, fast food, wrap, kolkata, bengali, indian, fry, onion, sauce, spicy",
        "pic": "recipeimages/egg-chicken-roll.jpg",
