        "add-pic-top": "recipeimages/chicken-stew-add-top.jpg",
        "ingrediants": "<ul><li>Half kg Chicken with bones.<\/li><li>1 onion, thinly sliced.<\/li><li>1 Teaspoon of fresh ginger and garlic paste.<\/li><li>Half of a tomato, chopped.<\/li><li>Vegetables (1 small potato, 6 pieces of raw papaya, sliced green beans, sliced bell peppers, sliced carrots etc).<\/li><li>Salt and Pepper powder.<\/li><li>A cube of butter.<\/li><li>3 Tablespoons of oil.<\/li><li>Whole spices (6 black peppercorns, 2 green cardamom, 3 cloves, 1 very small cinnamon stick).<\/li><li>Water.<\/li><li>2 green chilies.<\/li><li>Some chopped green onions or coriander leaves.<\/li><\/ul>"
