        "ingrediants": "<ul><li>Whole spices (2 green cardamom, 3 cloves, 6 black peppercorns, 2 Tablespoons of poppy seeds, 1 small cinnamon stick, 2 dry red chilies, 1 Tablespoon of coriander seeds, 1 Tablespoon of cumin seeds).<\/li><li>2 Tablespoons of curd.<\/li><li>1 onion, thinly sliced.<\/li><li>1 Tablespoon of chopped garlic.<\/li><li>Half Tablespoon of chopped ginger.<\/li><li>1 and half Teaspoon of turmeric powder.<\/li><li>1 Teaspoon of hot red chilli powder.<\/li><li>Salt and sugar.<\/li><li>3 Tablespoons of dried / fresh grated coconut.<\/li><li>4 Tablespoons of oil.<\/li><li>Warm water.<\/li><li>Half kg chicken with bone pieces.<\/li><\/ul>"
