        "ingrediants": "<ul><li>4 with bone fish pieces (rui / rohu / katla).<\/li><li>4 Teaspoons onion paste.<\/li><li>1 Teaspoon ginger paste.<\/li><li>3 Teaspoons hung curd.<\/li><li>3 Teaspoons turmeric powder.<\/li><li>1 Teaspoon cumin powder.<\/li><li>1 Teaspoon coriander powder.<\/li><li>half Teaspoons red chili powder.<\/li><li>Whole spices ( 1 small cinnamon stick, 3 green cardemoms, 3 cloves, 1 bay leaf)<\/li><li>Salt and sugar.<\/li><li>2 green chilies.<\/li><li>8 Teaspoons mustard oil.<\/li><li>Warm water.<\/li><li>1 Teaspoon ghee / clarified butter.<\/li><\/ul>"
